You will have full access to all the features of SkedPal during this period absolutely free with no obligation.

We do not ask for any payment details to get started for the 14-day free trial. In case, you do not wish to subscribe, there won’t be any charges or commitments.

There are many free task management apps with premium pricing of as little as $3/mo. There is a lot more to SkedPal than list management. The artificial intelligence used in the app makes you 10x more productive. Try it FREE now!

As soon as you’re ready to upgrade your account to a paid subscription plan, you can go to the app settings and subscribe to either the monthly or yearly plans.

You’ll be able to cancel your subscription at any time using the app settings. This will prevent your card from getting charged at the next billing cycle.

If you cancel before the end of your billing period, you can continue to enjoy SkedPal services up until your renewal date!

Yes, you can get up to 100% discount on your subscription cost by inviting your friends. For every friend who subscribes to SkedPal, we’ll give you both 10% discount.
